      • mutable

        public abstract MutableFloatMatrix<U> mutable()
        Create a mutable version of this FloatMatrix.
        The mutable version is created with a shallow copy of the data and the internal copyOnWrite flag set. The first operation in the mutable version that modifies the data shall trigger a deep copy of the data.
        Returns:
        MutableFloatMatrix; mutable version of this FloatMatrix

      • solve

        public static FloatVector<SIUnit> solve(FloatMatrix<?> A,
                        FloatVector<?> b)
                                 throws ValueException
        Solve x for A*x = b. According to Colt: x; a new independent matrix; solution if A is square, least squares solution if A.rows() > A.columns(), underdetermined system solution if A.rows() < A.columns().
        Parameters:
        A - matrix A in A*x = b
        b - vector b in A*x = b
        Returns:
        vector x in A*x = b
        Throws:
        ValueException - when Matrix A is neither Sparse nor Dense.
